[
  "Elisabeth Furtwaengler, daughter of publishing magnate Hubert Burda and doctor and actress Maria Furtwaengler, owns 25% of Burda Media Group.",
  "Its portfolio consists of some 600 media products in 24 countries, including Focus and Bunte and the German editions of Elle and Harper's Bazaar.",
  "She is a member of Burda Media's board of directors, as is her brother Jacob, and performs as a singer-songwriter under the stage name Lisa Fou.",
  "Before studying at a music conservatory in California, she studied art history at Cambridge University."
]